amics and population interactions in the NPSG. A comprehensive under-standing of the environmental controls on microbial rates and processes, from genomes to biomes, will be required to inform the scientific community and the public at large about the potential impacts of human-induced climate change. The pace of new discovery, and the importance of integrating this new knowl-edge into conceptual paradigms and predictive models, is an enormous contemporary challenge with great scientific and societal relevance.},
